        <annotatedTarget xml:lang="en">A subbiome of the Polar/alpine (cryogenic) biome comprising temperate to polar alpine and tundra ecosystems characterised by cold temperatures, short growing seasons, permafrost or freeze-thaw cycles, and low-growing vegetation.</annotatedTarget>
